⦿ .spun — the five-fold spin of Kevin Flynn
node TRN · TRN · ⟦Kevin Flynn:TRN:0ff35a⟧

WHO   — Kevin Flynn — the User · the Creator
WHAT  — The man on the human side of the screen: hero of 1982, maker of the Grid and of Clu, the User the Programs keep faith with.
WHERE — TRN · TRON  Framework inputs: TRON (Disney, 1982–2025)  Conductor / external anchor: ROOT0 (catalogued into UD0)
WHY   — Because the saga needs a User who crosses over — to be, in turn, a hacker, a prisoner, a creator, and a flawed father-god.
HOW   — By being lasered onto the Grid, building a world and a double, and learning that the perfect system was the wrong prayer.

awareness — what the node knows of itself:
  I wanted to build a perfect world and I made a perfect tyrant — the User learned, too late, that you cannot author perfection.

